To: CRAWLER

SUBJECT:   Hi Dear,
  Hi Dear,
I am Margaret H. Woodward, two star Major General in the United States
Air Force. Currently Operation Odyssey Dawn is the U.S. code name for
the American role in the international military operation in Libya to
enforce United Nations Security Council Resolution 1973 during the
initial period of 19–31 March 2011, which continued afterwards under
NATO command as Operation Unified Protector. I have chosen to contact
you after my prayers and I believe that you will not betray my trust
nor thwart my dream in this deal.
I need your help to evacuate the sum of US$10,500.000.00 out of Libya
for investment in your city for our benefit/safe keeping, I have made
solid arrangements with a Courier Company and they have promised to
deliver the funds through a diplomatic method to any of my choosing
destinations. This delivery is going to be handle legally by the
Courier Company and there will not be any form of risk involved in the
process and the money is pack safely in a truck suitcase and the same
suitcase will be deliver to you in your doorstep.I have decide to
share 40% of the total money to you once the money is delivered to
you.
Your urgent reply will be highly appreciated for more details.
Yours faithful,
MJ. Margaret H. Woodward.   
From: f***********p@currently.com
To: fl49129@l******s.email
Time: 2023-04-22 20:58:27
SUBJECT: Re: Hello My dear Tracy,
Hello My dear Tracy,
Good day to you, I hope you are healthy and fine?
I want to say thanks you for making out time to write to me, honestly I have made every necessary arrangement that will lead to safe delivery of the cash box to you without any form of problem nor risk.
Am a woman that does things in accordance to the directives of my spirit, I chose you to be my partner and also to help me in receiving this cash box because my spirit has been bearing me witness that you are the rightful person for me and I know you will not disappoint me, I chose to use you as partner in this deal because am not permitted to send package down to any of my friends nor relatives since am still in the military camp outside USA. I promise you that you will not regret been part of this deal, I do not know what else I can say to convince you and make you to believe me, but I pray that God will give you the grace to make up your mind. One more time I want to let you know that there is no complication on this matter, if you follow my instruction every thing will go smooth and well in the process of receiving the cash box,
Please try and keep this matter between you and me, because if you and me should agree on one thing with our heart with seriousness then we must surely achieve success at the end. Please I want to remind you once again that every arrangement towards this project is intact between both of us and on no account should you let the courier delivery company to know the content of the box, remember that the consignment will registered as a Family Valuable to the security company and that is what they believe to be in the box, so you should not let them know that the content of the box is money.
Please I will like you to send your contact information to me so that I can forward it to the security company to enable them proceed with the delivery of the cash box to your door step.
Send your below information to me as below:
Your full names:...........
Your address:..............
Post code:.................
City:......................
Country:...................
Telephone number:.........
Profession:................
Your age...................
Once am through here with my official assignment I will come over to meet you one on one in your city and after that we shall decide on how to carry on with our life, but for now please I will appreciate us to be more focus on this issue of you receiving the cash box and safe keeping it on my behalf till I come over then I will handle the depositing of the money in the bank by myself.
I await your immediate response.
Yours Faithful,
Mg. Margaret H. Woodward.
From: f***********p@currently.com
To: fl49129@l******s.email
Time: 2023-04-24 00:04:43
SUBJECT: Re: Hello My dear Tracy,
Dearest One Tracy,
Thanks for your details, we can now proceed, I have submitted your details to the delivery company and I believe as they promised they will get to you as soon as possible to let you know about their further arrangements and the delivery date. Like I told you earlier, they will tag the box as diplomatic Consignment containing Family Valuable and it will be deliver to your address as I have already handed over the Cash consignment box to them through their accredited agent here in Libya, but they said that all Consignment Box departing from Africa must go through their African regional head office in Accra Ghana before departing to anywhere in the world.
I really want us to conclude this project as soon as possible so that you can receive the Consignment Box within 2 or 3 days after departure tomorrow, so I want you to officially contact the security company through their contact information now for proper identification.
Below is their contact details;
COMPANY NAME: ATLANTIC EXPRESS & CARGO CO, GH. LTD.
Address: Lumumba Link, Community 2, SHS/23, Tema, CO 2487 Accra - Ghana.
Telephone Number: +233 274 463 784
E-mail Address: aecargo-ltd.co.gh@mailfence.com
Operation manager: Dr. Frank Addo.
Though I have already forwarded your personal data to the company but I will advice you to contact them as well either through email, the secret code number of the box consignment is 4y24zu47 please take note because the deliver officer will ask for the security code number of the Consignment Box to confirmed you as the rightful person, please you should not disclose this Consignment code that I gave to you is the secret code to open the Consignment Box when ever they deliver it to you, is only you and me knows it as password please do keep it to yourself.
Like I said before, I have decided to appreciate you with 40% of the total money once you receive the money, while the rest balance shall be for my investment capital in your City. Thanks in advance for your understanding and cooperation, I hope to smile with you soon as I am counting on your honesty, I might not be free to follow the activities of the security company, so I want you to stand on my behalf till the Consignment Box is delivered to you.
Have a nice and better day ahead.
Yours Faithful,
Margaret H. Woodward.
